    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to use of an ultrasonic humidifier to apply extremely small, finely controlled, amounts of dilute solutions to a material. In conservation this is typically an art object or artifact.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
